#id=1
#text=It was my girlfriend 's birthday so I baked her a cake .
#id=2
#text=It was nothing fancy , just a cake from a box .
#id=3
#text=I mixed all the ingredients together after I preheated the oven to the appropriate temperature .
#id=4
#text=After mixing the ingredients I poured them into a baking pan .
#id=5
#text=Then I put the pan in the oven .
#id=6
#text=While I waited for the cake to cook I made an icing to go on top .
#id=7
#text=I made it from cream cheese and strawberries which I whipped together with sugar .
#id=8
#text=Once the cake was done baking I pulled it from the oven and set it aside to cool .
#id=9
#text=After it was cool I frosted it with my homemade icing .
#text=Then I piped her name on top in fancy lettering .
#text=Once that was done I placed it on a fancy cake tray and waited for her to arrive home so we could eat the cake together .
